<body>
    <h1>T7 - Requirement Analysis Document</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"2d65358413b5">
<li local-id=3D"69eaa6a71068">
<p local-id=3D"06f3d8382eb6"><strong>Introduction</strong></p></li>
</ol>
<p local-id=3D"35a6e308a6ca"><strong>1.1 Purpose</strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"52d62d71c20a">This document defines the requirements for the=
 =E2=80=9CTemp Directory File Count Monitoring System.=E2=80=9D</p>
<p local-id=3D"bea69eee366d">The purpose of this system is to automatically=
 monitor the number of files present in a system temporary directory, publi=
sh the metric to a monitoring stack, visualize it in dashboards, and trigge=
r email alerts when thresholds are exceeded.</p>
<p local-id=3D"c69744eb5e02">This document is intended for:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"d41b5dcab5c2">
<li local-id=3D"6d2f1e396bc9">
<p local-id=3D"d8dd852bbd53">DevOps Engineers</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1a3fbeb52238">
<p local-id=3D"dfc1b5a74bfb">SRE Teams</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c69ec4a2c29d">
<p local-id=3D"3035fc454e33">Cloud Engineers</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a701c170f1ec">
<p local-id=3D"9a50e8f66a72">Project Reviewers</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4fc4b0a9b2a4">
<p local-id=3D"19e74968e023">System Administrators</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"28557240f294">It serves as a formal requirement analysis bef=
ore implementation and deployment.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"93ff6f91bff5">
<p local-id=3D"14a8e4f89d3a"><strong>1.2 Scope</strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"c6656bc64852"><strong>In Scope</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"50aa26bcda65">
<li local-id=3D"3677fc97423a">
<p local-id=3D"f8a9cdf4e560">Development of a file-count collector</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d9c5197ccfe2">
<p local-id=3D"b0e38bac6707">Deployment as AWS Lambda</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6b633ca17e09">
<p local-id=3D"f1bb4a0c1dc7">Scheduled execution using EventBridge</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e5414f57c95a">
<p local-id=3D"8beb55551b8e">Pushing metrics to Pushgateway</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"537551e2748f">
<p local-id=3D"8da027c8d750">Scraping via Prometheus (or compatible)</p></l=
i>
<li local-id=3D"183fb639f5f2">
<p local-id=3D"d11958eace4c">Visualization in Grafana</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"9597d9720b18">
<p local-id=3D"e1039e606471">Alerting via Grafana email notifications</p></=
li>
<li local-id=3D"5180f7daf744">
<p local-id=3D"4e377f8900aa">Optional containerization</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4a49df60c999">
<p local-id=3D"149850b312bd">Optional deployment to ECS Fargate</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"ab3b5125649f"><strong>Out of Scope</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"363d140efd94">
<li local-id=3D"25559f6ae3fb">
<p local-id=3D"bb223072e69c">Deep file system analysis (file sizes, types, =
content)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c75b9ce9adef">
<p local-id=3D"518bb8dcf268">Automated cleanup of temp directory</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"93807ebff05a">
<p local-id=3D"a3e103c92366">OS-level performance tuning</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"cdf1c2c308e2">
<p local-id=3D"7a615a3c836a">Enterprise-scale distributed file tracking</p>=
</li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"3cfffd40d03d">This system is strictly for monitoring and ale=
rting.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"02c52107cbd6">
<p local-id=3D"0b5378251e1d"><strong>1.3 Definitions, Acronyms, and Abbrevi=
ations</strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"b13a640705d1">Lambda =E2=80=93 AWS serverless compute servic=
e<br>
Pushgateway =E2=80=93 Prometheus component for pushing metrics<br>
Prometheus =E2=80=93 Time-series monitoring system<br>
Grafana =E2=80=93 Visualization and alerting platform<br>
ECS =E2=80=93 Elastic Container Service<br>
Fargate =E2=80=93 Serverless container compute for ECS<br>
SRE =E2=80=93 Site Reliability Engineering<br>
EventBridge =E2=80=93 AWS event scheduling service</p>
<hr local-id=3D"a5fa8fdfb390">
<p local-id=3D"4af5fe1a6fff"><strong>1.4 References</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"289624e30439">
<li local-id=3D"676176dfbea0">
<p local-id=3D"1473fb851240">AWS Lambda Documentation</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"89177958344d">
<p local-id=3D"00a96c482b95">AWS EventBridge Documentation</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"0109a4f644d7">
<p local-id=3D"a1071e15075b">Prometheus Pushgateway Documentation</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8326a1af2989">
<p local-id=3D"caf60de98ab1">Grafana Alerting Documentation</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"22d2f0a114ea">
<p local-id=3D"7cfdc739ff9e">ECS Fargate Documentation</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"afbfac35d644">
<p local-id=3D"7768f74111f9"><strong>1.5 Overview</strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"338b915d0700">This document describes:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"d329599d1880">
<li local-id=3D"6eb40f32c9b8">
<p local-id=3D"5a445a565354">Project objectives</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"88ca5d8d434d">
<p local-id=3D"7196cb3f7477">Functional requirements</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"127aa33961c3">
<p local-id=3D"4d97135b9cb6">Non-functional requirements</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ba260e810eb0">
<p local-id=3D"dc8d47cc5432">Architecture constraints</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ccfd3d86e1e1">
<p local-id=3D"d9be41937b91">Risk analysis</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"08db468ea78c">
<p local-id=3D"09a60384692d">Deployment assumptions</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"2a9e241d0578">
<ol start=3D"2" local-id=3D"a14ad1410ab9">
<li local-id=3D"ad4a8078b370">
<p local-id=3D"8dc6d37b29e3"><strong>Project Overview</strong></p></li>
</ol>
<p local-id=3D"116e21fdb673"><strong>2.1 Project Objectives</strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"30466b429f51">The main objectives are:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"6f1c1a8536ef">
<li local-id=3D"f12333c6033a">
<p local-id=3D"c7f528b9697a">Automate monitoring of temp directory file cou=
nt</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a075919dec9a">
<p local-id=3D"62308147f042">Ensure real-time visibility via dashboards</p>=
</li>
<li local-id=3D"8a666c3e1a71">
<p local-id=3D"cf3fc4bb5fcd">Prevent system performance issues caused by fi=
le accumulation</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"73c20fb9568b">
<p local-id=3D"2976b135dfcf">Trigger proactive alerts before operational de=
gradation</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"a4760432a2cf">
<p local-id=3D"694746af48d0"><strong>2.2 Business Goals</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"a6c6c4a4593e">
<li local-id=3D"a274be924037">
<p local-id=3D"95c4e7cd786c">Improve system observability</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"3254fc08079c">
<p local-id=3D"768b4a339273">Reduce operational risk due to unmonitored tem=
p growth</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"453531fcbbcc">
<p local-id=3D"582b8101c11a">Provide automated monitoring without manual in=
tervention</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4c172f98952d">
<p local-id=3D"bd2513ad96a2">Enable reusable monitoring architecture (conta=
iner-based deployment)</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"baf6606844bb">
<p local-id=3D"40560a951534"><strong>2.3 Background</strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"ecdcc76bd3b6">Temporary directories can accumulate excessive=
 files over time.</p>
<p local-id=3D"d2b1e2694930">If left unmonitored, this may cause:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"36e8a69dce72">
<li local-id=3D"cb539abdcb04">
<p local-id=3D"1d13d829e508">Disk space exhaustion</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"cb178890c640">
<p local-id=3D"b28726aceafa">Application failures</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"3affd83eef32">
<p local-id=3D"e07b2be24059">Performance degradation</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e780a838644a">
<p local-id=3D"2eb2def979af">System instability</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"07aa7cbf4b52">Currently, file count is not automatically mon=
itored.</p>
<p local-id=3D"b7a51ea4b832">This project introduces automated monitoring i=
ntegrated with modern observability tools.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"f87ff46491dd">
<p local-id=3D"b38f0281c6e8"><strong>2.4 Constraints</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"9ccbe153765d">
<li local-id=3D"f53e0fa25fc4">
<p local-id=3D"032058316e70">Must run within AWS ecosystem</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"0286f2fcc4e8">
<p local-id=3D"c11264cea431">Must use Pushgateway-compatible metric format<=
/p></li>
<li local-id=3D"5e4781b53c1c">
<p local-id=3D"90a25fa3b860">Must integrate with existing Grafana setup</p>=
</li>
<li local-id=3D"fc07f98c8f22">
<p local-id=3D"0871a908e4ef">Lambda execution timeout limitations</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ecce0642188b">
<p local-id=3D"cbf2daec4cd9">Network connectivity required to Pushgateway</=
p></li>
<li local-id=3D"2b10dc2b3f13">
<p local-id=3D"8c051d14b388">Budget constraints for AWS compute services</p=
></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"5dc1db883780">
<ol start=3D"3" local-id=3D"ded09ea82363">
<li local-id=3D"5af188b32138">
<p local-id=3D"fc970e09e7ee"><strong>Functional Requirements</strong></p></=
li>
</ol>
<p local-id=3D"4ce8d1f5c53d"><strong>3.1 Use Case Diagram</strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"e7439b92ce25">Actors:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"21e9bb7c17ad">
<li local-id=3D"91f9549fbdd9">
<p local-id=3D"34c10cf66fa7">Scheduler (EventBridge)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"eff1f2a7efff">
<p local-id=3D"38dd2db71c56">Collector (Lambda or Container)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"2baf0a84b263">
<p local-id=3D"dec893b6609f">Pushgateway</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"80131dbb1394">
<p local-id=3D"cf181115e44e">Prometheus</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1060410124d2">
<p local-id=3D"1c10e76fba0c">Grafana</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e70def5aed04">
<p local-id=3D"2022e827554b">System Administrator (Email Recipient)</p></li=
>
</ul><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper c=
onfluence-embedded-manual-size"><img class=3D"confluence-embedded-image ima=
ge-center" alt=3D"image-20260309-185515.png" width=3D"468" loading=3D"lazy"=
 src=3D"ceb30f85a6f2fdb1f7d5cf9db2f51574c87722442266ce6a4ef83ba08c598385" d=
ata-image-src=3D"https://iamops.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/181=
5577131/image-20260309-185515.png?version=3D1&amp;modificationDate=3D177308=
2518275&amp;cacheVersion=3D1&amp;api=3Dv2" data-height=3D"2128" data-width=
=3D"3476" data-unresolved-comment-count=3D"0" data-linked-resource-id=3D"18=
43134663" data-linked-resource-version=3D"1" data-linked-resource-type=3D"a=
ttachment" data-linked-resource-default-alias=3D"image-20260309-185515.png"=
 data-base-url=3D"https://iamops.atlassian.net/wiki" data-linked-resource-c=
ontent-type=3D"image/png" data-linked-resource-container-id=3D"1815577131" =
data-linked-resource-container-version=3D"3" data-media-id=3D"6ad9cf93-3a5a=
-49d1-bab8-414d05776031" data-media-type=3D"file" height=3D"286"></span>
<hr local-id=3D"00a078101043">
<p local-id=3D"819b176db1f3"><strong>3.2 Use Cases</strong></p>
<hr local-id=3D"f0a2d762118c">
<p local-id=3D"fd79317dbcfe"><strong>3.2.1 Use Case 1: Execute Scheduled Co=
llector</strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"5affaf1542c6">Description:<br>
Collector runs automatically on defined schedule.</p>
<p local-id=3D"d9377517b6f6">Actors:<br>
EventBridge, Lambda</p>
<p local-id=3D"66fb42ed0cd6">Preconditions:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"839af61062f8">
<li local-id=3D"219f3de3ca56">
<p local-id=3D"c3b3cf4885e4">Lambda deployed</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"5fa21c058919">
<p local-id=3D"d9662b5c8c31">IAM permissions configured</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"67f3dd4f01db">Postconditions:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"15c4086dbe10">
<li local-id=3D"9b6113fc6120">
<p local-id=3D"72c7177b3e82">Collector execution completed</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"5361289d853c">
<p local-id=3D"79d78bbaf585">File count calculated</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"77130206a45c">Flow of Events:</p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"2d0c7e32c73b">
<li local-id=3D"548127ac29a7">
<p local-id=3D"ed97f9da050c">EventBridge triggers Lambda.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"528dd194879a">
<p local-id=3D"423e2093c49b">Lambda reads environment variables.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"5a9dd65b4959">
<p local-id=3D"8e7651b121b8">Lambda accesses configured temp directory.</p>=
</li>
<li local-id=3D"66ba398edb9c">
<p local-id=3D"6cb569d0695a">Lambda counts number of files.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6fdd5607c9dd">
<p local-id=3D"347ddec2fd38">Logs count result.</p></li>
</ol>
<p local-id=3D"943fa218f60d">Alternative Flows:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"15edfc30b4a6">
<li local-id=3D"8c551da0b8ec">
<p local-id=3D"9adeceb67acd">Directory does not exist =E2=86=92 Log error, =
exit gracefully.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1f0435b2c433">
<p local-id=3D"514f9fe65807">Permission denied =E2=86=92 Log error.</p></li=
>
<li local-id=3D"e3ec62eff134">
<p local-id=3D"ff113217ccef">Execution timeout =E2=86=92 Mark failure in lo=
gs.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"edd3057b3472">
<p local-id=3D"762e4d0ae1eb"><strong>3.2.2 Use Case 2: Push Metric to Pushg=
ateway</strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"ed98e357f37b">Description:<br>
Collector pushes metric to Pushgateway.</p>
<p local-id=3D"d534bbf82585">Actors:<br>
Lambda, Pushgateway</p>
<p local-id=3D"017f2525ed25">Preconditions:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"a4b4e3c7a3ad">
<li local-id=3D"83539a190ac4">
<p local-id=3D"8d7feb77d2a2">File count successfully computed</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4fb1df14f757">
<p local-id=3D"dacc84fce0c3">Pushgateway reachable</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"310ce5a68130">Postconditions:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"597103456ff9">
<li local-id=3D"41dfa3cb768a">
<p local-id=3D"b4fba3e2c339">Metric temp_dir_file_count updated</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"27b96dabd191">Flow of Events:</p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"3fc8104226d8">
<li local-id=3D"b55e0abec2d0">
<p local-id=3D"d120f7f99ffd">Collector formats metric in Prometheus format.=
</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"28b91d06adcc">
<p local-id=3D"496baa306849">Collector sends HTTP POST to Pushgateway.</p><=
/li>
<li local-id=3D"060adaaad560">
<p local-id=3D"f94880a6b509">Pushgateway stores metric.</p></li>
</ol>
<p local-id=3D"81dea1b05114">Alternative Flows:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"73dab153e9e2">
<li local-id=3D"a799c6f5b096">
<p local-id=3D"7a8555bb9f08">Network failure =E2=86=92 Log error.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"93b85cc59913">
<p local-id=3D"97c038359bb1">Push failure =E2=86=92 Retry (optional).</p></=
li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"b5418b126d81">
<p local-id=3D"c9193bb2ce58"><strong>3.2.3 Use Case 3: Visualize Metric in =
Grafana</strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"8a2cdaaf025e">Description:<br>
Metric is displayed in dashboard panels.</p>
<p local-id=3D"a5ae3206928f">Actors:<br>
Prometheus, Grafana</p>
<p local-id=3D"b76a438afa34">Preconditions:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"d0d534865cfa">
<li local-id=3D"cf8afd22b88d">
<p local-id=3D"d91ce4598354">Prometheus scraping Pushgateway</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"adffba9a0f9e">
<p local-id=3D"9d5240a143aa">Grafana connected to Prometheus</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"698ff868910d">Postconditions:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"6f9b1cad564c">
<li local-id=3D"dbe2dd2b7470">
<p local-id=3D"6880c9490335">Time-series graph visible</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e85a83675943">
<p local-id=3D"e8c8bd5b7fc9">Stat panel shows current count</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"485b6f505844">
<p local-id=3D"41cff8dfcf01"><strong>3.2.4 Use Case 4: Alert When Threshold=
 Exceeded</strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"cf6120aea4fd">Description:<br>
Send email alert if file count exceeds 100 for defined duration.</p>
<p local-id=3D"8a5f1a6cbbc8">Actors:<br>
Grafana, Email System</p>
<p local-id=3D"1b213fd68893">Preconditions:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"11b53ed0c3f8">
<li local-id=3D"9d317fbc1318">
<p local-id=3D"06ce9475a7cd">Alert rule configured</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"21ac1f4af9d9">
<p local-id=3D"d131a4fa9cf9">Email contact point configured</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"00cb47cca2dc">Postconditions:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"c9870a2946a4">
<li local-id=3D"64e2b3dad46b">
<p local-id=3D"60e1e67fdfe2">Email notification sent to configured recipien=
t</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"10d941fdc088">Flow:</p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"fc50cc1db8d2">
<li local-id=3D"d1b5fc41ea19">
<p local-id=3D"3067bacbdd5c">Grafana evaluates rule.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4ff466a249a2">
<p local-id=3D"1cabcee682ab">If temp_dir_file_count &gt; 100 for 5=E2=80=93=
10 minutes:</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b50cc391b8e4">
<p local-id=3D"6c3954fec258">Trigger alert.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"29f43ad76bf9">
<p local-id=3D"5c6ac35f1866">Send email including:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"84115a6cd010">
<li local-id=3D"f6575a5ec530">
<p local-id=3D"7cd7cc7ce0cb">Directory path</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"36edc2fac95c">
<p local-id=3D"c1c2e2cb712f">Current count</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"173c20d51b47">
<p local-id=3D"6b5255607af4">Timestamp</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"7ec3c767788c">
<p local-id=3D"9ff669ffa537">Labels</p></li>
</ul></li>
</ol>
<hr local-id=3D"d909df63465e">
<p local-id=3D"f63a589b99be"><strong>3.2.5 Use Case 5 (Bonus): Deploy Conta=
iner Version</strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"7155989ccf9e">Description:<br>
Collector packaged as container and deployed to:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"3ccfe580052a">
<li local-id=3D"585fb73ae701">
<p local-id=3D"8d64aeaf6073">Lambda (container-based)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1cdf301a1bed">
<p local-id=3D"c2ea6f6b354f">ECS Fargate</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"cb86c96a4582">Preconditions:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"12f27fe75c2b">
<li local-id=3D"37f326e34480">
<p local-id=3D"201739273f88">Docker image built</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"7a132f29db32">
<p local-id=3D"a48b1f940bce">Image stored in ECR</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"2a2e280850b6">
<p local-id=3D"a97e2bdec886">IAM roles configured</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"c6659a1fba00">Postconditions:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"277beb79fb24">
<li local-id=3D"ef19e0624d49">
<p local-id=3D"3ed7ab37725f">Container runs successfully</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"fa1c892ecf74">
<p local-id=3D"afce660a0a3b">Metrics pushed</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"61a16332d880">
<ol start=3D"4" local-id=3D"86e136b87aa2">
<li local-id=3D"cc46b6b2f494">
<p local-id=3D"ef24b67fdb2a"><strong>Non-Functional Requirements</strong></=
p></li>
</ol>
<p local-id=3D"d3e2809c510b"><strong>4.1 Performance Requirements</strong><=
/p>
<ul local-id=3D"a11bfa73d1bc">
<li local-id=3D"7cbff5821237">
<p local-id=3D"72a0d5ae261f">Lambda execution must complete within configur=
ed timeout.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8c8212150029">
<p local-id=3D"cde132e53d86">Metric push must complete within 5 seconds.</p=
></li>
<li local-id=3D"c26d4c2f0bfb">
<p local-id=3D"376c0d19fad2">System must support execution frequency of 1=
=E2=80=935 minutes.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d084c41d424d">
<p local-id=3D"706c8a64c569">Dashboard refresh latency &lt; 30 seconds.</p>=
</li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"52030408c207">
<p local-id=3D"8797b263950b"><strong>4.2 Security Requirements</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"76f5085db6e5">
<li local-id=3D"c8df8cc27a24">
<p local-id=3D"2e9832aee7aa">IAM least-privilege policy.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"18354db5c787">
<p local-id=3D"3287590bcab6">Secure network communication (HTTPS).</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"64b88837c250">
<p local-id=3D"562a0e28e527">Pushgateway access restricted via security gro=
ups.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f15ae1841b99">
<p local-id=3D"eaefb4ae08d2">No hardcoded credentials in code.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"26dc5d358636">
<p local-id=3D"df17ae495e23">Environment variables used for configuration.<=
/p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"5b68038d7e65">
<p local-id=3D"8111f0e9cafa"><strong>4.3 Usability Requirements</strong></p=
>
<ul local-id=3D"099ed2f3fc39">
<li local-id=3D"7c09626bdd59">
<p local-id=3D"04a98d02f807">Dashboard must clearly display:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"836db2f0b4ea">
<li local-id=3D"385c93df08d9">
<p local-id=3D"bac09d6de7e7">Time-series graph</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"abe3220cc695">
<p local-id=3D"db8450a3ae4e">Current file count</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"e7ef936de220">
<p local-id=3D"9a27e82b69f3">Alert message must contain actionable informat=
ion.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"9c22e83bc154">
<p local-id=3D"9fb901a8c644">Configuration must be easily modifiable via en=
vironment variables.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"9d4b950865ce">
<p local-id=3D"94f5e70585be"><strong>4.4 Reliability Requirements</strong><=
/p>
<ul local-id=3D"9da41211a590">
<li local-id=3D"1a2f70ae249f">
<p local-id=3D"0e857234451e">Lambda failure should be logged in CloudWatch.=
</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"135625f3a707">
<p local-id=3D"5c3cb90076d0">System should tolerate temporary Pushgateway u=
navailability.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"80f333b3ad79">
<p local-id=3D"f02f4638281c">Alert evaluation window prevents noise (5=E2=
=80=9310 minutes threshold).</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"de247733f588">
<p local-id=3D"3001079eb3a5"><strong>4.5 Compliance Requirements</strong></=
p>
<ul local-id=3D"0c71e0b94cc1">
<li local-id=3D"0deb3f135d5c">
<p local-id=3D"2ef22392b10e">Must comply with AWS security best practices.<=
/p></li>
<li local-id=3D"04349546229c">
<p local-id=3D"6400c2c38488">Logging retained as per organization policy.</=
p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8976adf4d8e5">
<p local-id=3D"faa0663da717">No sensitive data stored in metrics.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"bbfc7b4398c0">
<ol start=3D"5" local-id=3D"0f980ce335e1">
<li local-id=3D"747c2e3231c6">
<p local-id=3D"993a27a72947"><strong>Assumptions and Dependencies</strong><=
/p></li>
</ol>
<p local-id=3D"e0adc66fe564"><strong>5.1 Assumptions</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"a6d2e4445e05">
<li local-id=3D"80241ffeffd8">
<p local-id=3D"d234490304f9">Temp directory path exists.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e201ddf4820e">
<p local-id=3D"11707d0e2e10">Pushgateway is reachable.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"92816b2fa290">
<p local-id=3D"6aa66d84b5bb">Prometheus is properly scraping Pushgateway.</=
p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c9d6818c58b5">
<p local-id=3D"f4b85cee1efb">Grafana email configuration works.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"04c73bb5cf22">
<p local-id=3D"dbc4534b9f6c">AWS permissions are correctly configured.</p><=
/li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"308ba96cc93e">
<p local-id=3D"ecc511638c96"><strong>5.2 Dependencies</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"dd6cb505128d">
<li local-id=3D"2e64371839d1">
<p local-id=3D"a28d9b02a1c6">AWS Lambda</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d07a17104b31">
<p local-id=3D"4be5ed09a2ca">EventBridge Scheduler</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"21ef77d4d5ea">
<p local-id=3D"9be8f4387474">Pushgateway</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1fd216391a39">
<p local-id=3D"2759f59b0ffb">Prometheus</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a15ae93c0985">
<p local-id=3D"e23a76f32ef2">Grafana</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"268b74c27b36">
<p local-id=3D"698df323599a">SMTP or Grafana Cloud alerting</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"631cb199e40a">
<p local-id=3D"5a3af45dbe9b">(Bonus) ECS Fargate + ECR</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"ff523a795589">
<ol start=3D"6" local-id=3D"2ca7aaedbaee">
<li local-id=3D"65e357d7b2cf">
<p local-id=3D"fb81cf2b7c76"><strong>Risk Analysis</strong></p></li>
</ol>
<p local-id=3D"7609a5c9f986"><strong>6.1 Risk Identification</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"bdfaa16fc152">
<li local-id=3D"872639be96b6">
<p local-id=3D"7f9c943851b9">Network connectivity failure</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"29112be1ef9a">
<p local-id=3D"08c04f98bee1">Pushgateway downtime</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4d45e013ac64">
<p local-id=3D"361c95be40a4">Lambda timeout</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b0068c59db91">
<p local-id=3D"fab582618832">Incorrect IAM configuration</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a1e4942e7af0">
<p local-id=3D"1005ea064c35">Alert noise (false positives)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"aa3fd110854e">
<p local-id=3D"e2ed9368ea85">Misconfigured scrape interval</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"a9ead199eb9c">
<p local-id=3D"02ef6076afed"><strong>6.2 Risk Mitigation</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"488454c1a816">
<li local-id=3D"ae53dbb380e1">
<p local-id=3D"d1587794d52f">Implement structured logging</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4015ba404271">
<p local-id=3D"4876ba774afe">Use sustained alert window (5=E2=80=9310 minut=
es)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"9ef39a8eed0d">
<p local-id=3D"6c8a44ff75fc">Use retries for metric push</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6c146c00c013">
<p local-id=3D"c284ff4ad255">Validate IAM roles before deployment</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1da6673b02d7">
<p local-id=3D"2435a552fa38">Test alert threshold using simulated load</p><=
/li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"7d8e45fc8b05">
<ol start=3D"7" local-id=3D"de999e3a2c6d">
<li local-id=3D"9a64a0c422e9">
<p local-id=3D"7aff2f0620b3"><strong>Glossary</strong></p></li>
</ol>
<p local-id=3D"c9c4edea3cca">Metric =E2=80=93 Numeric measurement exported =
to monitoring system<br>
Scraping =E2=80=93 Pull-based metric collection by Prometheus<br>
Push Model =E2=80=93 Metric pushed to gateway instead of pulled directly<br=
>
Threshold =E2=80=93 Value above which alert triggers</p>
<hr local-id=3D"baa574153382">
<ol start=3D"8" local-id=3D"3f7cc9bdc090">
<li local-id=3D"58a538e1017b">
<p local-id=3D"3b14089b151a"><strong>Appendices</strong></p></li>
</ol>
<ul local-id=3D"87da0aaf50fc">
<li local-id=3D"321637286419">
<p local-id=3D"fcdd3f9c0ce1">Architecture Diagram</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"3a9953f1cffe">
<p local-id=3D"555518d44430">Use Case Diagram</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b89cb6e7699e">
<p local-id=3D"7803aee055e5">Deployment Screenshots</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"cf11b3ca4faa">
<p local-id=3D"8697aadbb292">Test Evidence</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"3745791a7a65">
<p local-id=3D"0f6aed1a9f44">Sample Alert Email Screenshot</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"78faebc15023">
<ol start=3D"9" local-id=3D"3746679a37c4">
<li local-id=3D"fe164b55d395">
<p local-id=3D"902bbaa6ba5d"><strong>Customer Acknowledgement</strong></p><=
/li>
</ol>
<p local-id=3D"dc0d42cf719c">Name:<br>
Title:<br>
Signature:<br>
Date:</p>
    </div>
</body>
